{"tid":2246637,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"人大常委會通過修改國旗法及國徽法，不得隨意丟棄國旗","createTime":"2020-10-17T08:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T10:04:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5b172fec4aff7859e838935b36e294fe896e13d2","tid":2246637,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T08:39:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555283-20201017.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555283-20201017.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24hao5WZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=b9a49e8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555283-20201017.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b4213f5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555283-20201017.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在北京，全國人大常委會下午表決通過關於修改國旗法、國徽法的決定，明年1月1日起實施。<br />\n<br />\n内地傳媒報道，修改後的國旗法、國徽法，進一步禁止損害國旗和國徽尊嚴的行為。其中國旗法規定，不得倒掛、倒插或以其他有損國旗尊嚴的方式升掛和使用國旗，亦不得隨意丟棄國旗。<br />\n<br />\n修改後的法律規定，在公共場合故意以焚燒、毀損、塗劃、玷污、踐踏等方式侮辱國旗、國徽，依法追究刑事責任，情節較輕則由公安機關處以15日以下拘留。<br />\n<br />\n另外，法律亦增加國旗、國徽的適用場合，例如規定中央政府駐香港、澳門有關機構，應當在工作日升掛國旗並懸掛國徽。"},{"pid":"65c45470ebfe4b6338d4d3eb4f8a72e9287f0a53","tid":2246637,"uid":231583,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fba89a9412397999754da44c43532fe0c0ad2700","tid":2246637,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T08:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kvSTxhO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkvSTxhO.gif&h=948232c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfb0631d10a57eb156e3d61429c81d86862cd50a","tid":2246637,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c45470ebfe4b6338d4d3eb4f8a72e9287f0a53","tid":2246637,"uid":231583,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"